'''吉蓮娜·諾拉·“吉吉”·哈蒂德'''（{{lang-en|Jelena Noura "Gigi" Hadid}}，{{bd|1995年|4月23日|catIdx=Hadid, Gigi}}）<ref name="YolandaFamily">{{cite web |url=https://www.yolanda.com/about/my-family |title=My Family |work=Yolanda |first=Yolanda |last=Foster |accessdate=2014-04-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150801202931/http://www.yolanda.com/about/my-family |archivedate=2015-08-01 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vogue.com.tw/feature/horoscope/content-529.html|title=健康陽光模特兒二代 吉吉哈蒂德Gigi Hadid 4月23號生日|work=Vogue|author=Minnie Sun|date=2014-11-28|accessdate=2015-03-20|archive-date=2018-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181220035427/https://www.vogue.com.tw/feature/horoscope/content-529.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是一名[[阿拉伯裔美国人|阿拉伯裔]]、[[荷兰裔美国人|荷兰裔]]的美國模特兒。曾於2014年獲選為《[[運動畫刊泳裝特輯|運動畫刊泳裝特輯]]》的最佳新秀，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20140704/427763/|title=獲Tom Ford青睞　19歲辣模全裸噴香|work=蘋果日報|author=吳惠菁|date=2014-07-04|accessdate=2015-03-19|archive-date=2017-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170519113005/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20140704/427763/|dead-url=no}}</ref>她登上過幾次《[[比弗利娇妻|比弗利娇妻]]》節目。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bravotv.com/blogs/the-dish/yolanda-fosters-daughter-lands-coveted-swimsuit-issue-spot|title=Gigi Hadid is named one of 12 rookies in Sports Illustrated's annual issue.|work=Bravo TV|first=Sabrina|last=Ford|date=2014-02-04|accessdate=2014-04-05|archive-date=2015-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150702111616/http://www.bravotv.com/the-daily-dish/yolanda-fosters-daughter-lands-coveted-swimsuit-issue-spot|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

哈蒂德曾經登上《{{le|VMAN|VMAN}}》、《[[ELLE|ELLE]]》、《{{le|Grazia|Grazia}}》、《{{le|Cleo (magazine)|Cleo (雜誌)|Cleo}}》、《[[時尚_(雜誌)|時尚]]》、<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.glammonitor.com/2014/09/18/gigi-hadid-opens-eyes-israeli-palestinian-conflict/| title=Gigi Hadid Opens Our Eyes to the Israeli-Palestinian Conflict| work=The GlamMonitor| first=AnnaMarie| last=Houlis| date=2014-09-18| access-date=2015-03-19| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150315041109/http://www.glammonitor.com/2014/09/18/gigi-hadid-opens-eyes-israeli-palestinian-conflict/| archive-date=2015-03-15| dead-url=yes}}</ref>《[[運動畫刊|運動畫刊]]》、《{{le|Paper (雜誌)|Paper (magazine)|Paper}}》、《[[Schön!Magazine|美麗！]]》等雜誌。她自2012年起為[[盖尔斯|Guess]]代言至今。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20150123/547461/|title=星二代S曲線大辣　加持Guess春夏廣告|work=蘋果日報|author=劉妍伶|date=2015-01-23|accessdate=2015-03-19|archive-date=2017-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170810210001/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20150123/547461/|dead-url=no}}</ref>她亦是《Galore》雜誌與[[卡琳·洛菲德|卡琳·洛菲德]]的《CR Fashion Book》在2014年的封面模特兒，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://crfashionbook.com/post/76135702133/issue-4-preview-fairy-tales-a-first-look-at-our |title=ISSUE 4 PREVIEW: FAIRY TALES |work=CR Fashion Book |first= |last= |date=2014-02 |accessdate=2014-04-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140824085029/http://crfashionbook.com/post/76135702133/issue-4-preview-fairy-tales-a-first-look-at-our |archivedate=2014-08-24 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://fashionista.com/2014/02/gigi-hamid-cr-fashion-book-cover/|title=Real Housewives of Beverly Hills Offspring Gigi Hadid Scores CR Fashion Book Cover|work=Fashion Ista|first=Alyssa|last=Vingan|date=2014-02-07|accessdate=2014-04-05|archive-date=2014-03-19|archive-url=https://archive.today/20140319194346/http://fashionista.com/2014/02/gigi-hamid-cr-fashion-book-cover/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://galoremag.com/gigi-hadid-gets-gritty-for-our-2014-calendar/|title=Gigi Gets Gritty For Our 2014 Calendar|work=Galore Mag|first=Galore|last=Mag|date=2013-12-11|accessdate=2014-04-05|archive-date=2014-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140208062354/https://galoremag.com/gigi-hadid-gets-gritty-for-our-2014-calendar/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>並且於2014年3月登上《[[Schön!Magazine|美麗！]]》雜誌封面。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://schonmagazine.com/schon24/|title=Gigi Hadid Schon Magazine Cover|work=Schon Magazine|first=Schon|last=Mag|date=2014-03-27|accessdate=2014-04-05|archive-date=2014-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140401154621/http://schonmagazine.com/schon24|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wetpaint.com/real-housewives-of-beverly-hills/gallery/2014-03-27-gigi-hadid-leather-lace-schon/|title=Gigi Hadid Wears Leather and Lace in Sultry Rock ‘n’ Roll Photoshoot|work=Wet Paint|first=Jager|last=Weatherby|date=2014-03-27|accessdate=2014-04-05|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006140610/http://www.wetpaint.com/real-housewives-of-beverly-hills/gallery/2014-03-27-gigi-hadid-leather-lace-schon|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==早年生活與家族==
1995年4月23日，哈蒂德出生於[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]][[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]，父親是[[巴勒斯坦人|巴勒斯坦]][[地產發展商|不動產發展商]]{{le|穆罕默德·哈蒂德|Mohamed Hadid}}，母親為前[[荷蘭人|荷蘭]]模特兒{{le|約蘭達·福斯特|Yolanda Foster}}。吉吉有兩位弟妹：同是模特兒的妹妹[[貝拉·哈蒂德|貝拉]]（Bella）與弟弟安瓦爾（Anwar）。在她的父母離婚後，她的母親嫁給了[[音樂製作人|音樂製作人]][[大衛·佛斯特|大衛·佛斯特]]，成為了她的繼父。<ref name="YolandaFamily"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2232488/Gigi-Hadid-Real-Housewives-Yolanda-Foster-advises-daughter-17-needs-skinny-side.html|title=Yolanda Advises Daughter|work=Daily Mail|author=Daily Mail Reporter|date=2012-11-13|accessdate=2014-04-05|archive-date=2021-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210218222140/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2232488/Gigi-Hadid-Real-Housewives-Yolanda-Foster-advises-daughter-17-needs-skinny-side.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>她在2013年18歲時從{{le|馬里布高中|Malibu High School}}畢業，她在該校曾是排球校隊的隊長及一位具有競爭力的馬術騎師。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blog.kymberlymarciano.com/2013/07/interview-gigi-hadid-guess-girl.html|work=Kymberly Marciano Photography|title=Interview: Gigi Hadid, Guess Girl|first=Kymberley|last=Marciano|date=2013-07-18|accessdate=2014-04-05|archive-date=2020-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200821040540/http://blog.kymberlymarciano.com/2013/07/interview-gigi-hadid-guess-girl.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.maxpreps.com/athlete/gigi-hadid/Oli5yfTmEeKZ5AAmVebBJg/gendersport/volleyball-stats.htm|title=Gigi Hadid's Volleyball Stats|work=Max Preps|first=|last=|date=|accessdate=2014-04-05|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006121206/http://www.maxpreps.com/athlete/gigi-hadid/Oli5yfTmEeKZ5AAmVebBJg/gendersport/volleyball-stats.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| title= Do You Know Who Gigi Hadid Is?| work= Vanity Fair| first= Bennett| last= Marcus| date= 2014-02-10| url= http://www.vanityfair.com/online/daily/2014/02/gigi-hadid-interview| accessdate= 2014-04-05| archive-date= 2015-08-21| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150821234722/http://www.vanityfair.com/style/2014/02/gigi-hadid-interview| dead-url= no}}</ref>

她在高中畢業後搬到了[[紐約|紐約]]，專心致力於課業與模特兒生涯。之後，她在2013年秋季進入[[新學院|新學院]]就讀。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wetpaint.com/real-housewives-of-beverly-hills/articles/2013-11-18-where-gigi-yolanda-daughter-college|title=Where Does Gigi, Yolanda Foster’s Daughter, Go to College?|work=Wet Paint|first=Carson|last=Blackwelder|date=2014-02-17|accessdate=2014-04-05|archive-date=2014-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140402082011/http://www.wetpaint.com/real-housewives-of-beverly-hills/articles/2013-11-18-where-gigi-yolanda-daughter-college|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==職業生涯==
哈蒂德於2011年與{{le|IMG模特兒公司|IMG Models}}簽約。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.stylecaster.com/gigi-hadid|title=Why Model Gigi Hadid is Being Called the Next Kate Upton|work=Style Caster|first=Leah|last=Bourne|date=2014-02-14|accessdate=2014-06-05|archive-date=2014-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140526080836/http://www.stylecaster.com/gigi-hadid/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>她在年僅兩歲時被[[盖尔斯|Guess]]的{{le|保羅·馬西亞諾|Paul Marciano}}相中，展開了她的模特兒生涯。當時，她開始在Baby Guess擔任模特兒。她在之後中斷了這份工作，以專心致力於課業。最終，她又再回到模特兒圈，繼續與他們合作，且在2012年開始為Guess代言。據她最近接受採訪時表示，她在成年後已經為Guess出席了三場代言活動。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vanityfair.com/online/daily/2014/02/gigi-hadid-interview|title=Do You Know Who Gigi Hadid is|work=Vanity Fair|first=Bennett|last=Marcus|date=2014-02-10|accessdate=2014-04-05|archive-date=2015-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150821234722/http://www.vanityfair.com/style/2014/02/gigi-hadid-interview|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/475761/real-housewives-of-beverly-hills-star-yolanda-foster-s-daughter-gigi-hadid-models-for-guess-see-the-pretty-pic|title=Watch Gigi Hadid Walk the Catwalk During New York Fashion Week|work=E! Online|first=Ryan|last=Gajewski|date=2014-02-12|accessdate=2014-04-05|archive-date=2014-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413213258/http://www.eonline.com/news/475761/real-housewives-of-beverly-hills-star-yolanda-foster-s-daughter-gigi-hadid-models-for-guess-see-the-pretty-pic|dead-url=no}}</ref>她在2014年2月首次出席[[紐約時裝周|紐約時裝周]]，在西班牙休閒服飾品牌{{le|Desigual|Desigual}}的時裝展上走秀。她同時也登上了美國時裝設計師{{le|傑瑞米·史考特|Jeremy Scott}}時裝展的伸展臺。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wetpaint.com/real-housewives-of-beverly-hills/articles/2014-02-12-gigi-hadid-catwalk-fashion-week|title=Introducing Gigi Hadid, NYFW's Breakout Model Of The Season|work=Wet Paint|first=Maura|last=Brannigan|date=2014-02-12|accessdate=2014-04-05|archive-date=2014-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140426144506/http://www.wetpaint.com/real-housewives-of-beverly-hills/articles/2014-02-12-gigi-hadid-catwalk-fashion-week|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.luckymag.com/style/2014/02/gigi-hadid-model-nyfw-fall|title=Introducing Gigi Hadid, NYFW's Breakout Model Of The Season|work=Lucky Mag|first=Maura|last=Brannigan|date=|accessdate=2014-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140308033734/http://www.luckymag.com/style/2014/02/gigi-hadid-model-nyfw-fall|archive-date=2014-03-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url= http://www.realitytea.com/2014/02/10/gigi-hadid-walks-the-runways-of-ny-fashion-week-plus-kristen-doute-writing-a-memoir/| title= Gigi Hadid Walks The Runways of NY Fashion Week. Plus, Kristen Doute Writing A Memoir!| work= Reality Tea| author= Mary| date= 2014-02-10| accessdate= 2014-04-05| archive-date= 2014-03-05| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140305150840/http://www.realitytea.com/2014/02/10/gigi-hadid-walks-the-runways-of-ny-fashion-week-plus-kristen-doute-writing-a-memoir/| dead-url= yes}}</ref>她曾參與澳洲歌手[[寇弟·辛普森|寇弟·辛普森]]在2014年4月14日發行的〈Surfboard〉的音樂錄影帶演出。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2604844/Sports-Illustrated-model-Gigi-Hadid-sizzles-sultry-white-swimsuit-cosies-boyfriend-Cody-Simpson-new-Surfboard-music-video.html/|title=All grown up! Sports Illustrated model Gigi Hadid sizzles in low-cut cream swimsuit as she cosies up to boyfriend Cody Simpson in his Surfboard music video|work=Mail Online|first=Alicia|last=Vrajlal|date=2014-04-15|accessdate=2014-04-15|archive-date=2017-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170508185357/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2604844/Sports-Illustrated-model-Gigi-Hadid-sizzles-sultry-white-swimsuit-cosies-boyfriend-Cody-Simpson-new-Surfboard-music-video.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>她也曾出演另一部音樂錄影帶，美國葛萊美獎歌手{{le|馬吉爾 (歌手)|Miguel (singer)|馬吉爾}}在2014年5月29日發行的〈Simplethings〉。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hollywoodlife.com/2014/05/30/miguel-gigi-hadid-simplethings-music-video-cody-simpson/|title=Gigi H