er two public sightings|accessdate=2014-11-25|date=2014-11-27|archive-date=2016-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160118101158/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2848982/Gigi-Hadid-confirms-s-rekindled-love-Cody-Simpson-two-public-sightings.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>自此之後，兩人曾多次被捕捉到一同出席公開場合，甚至還與他們的朋友[[坎達兒·珍娜|坎達兒·珍娜]]及[[賽琳娜·戈梅茲|賽琳娜·戈梅茲]]一起在[[杜拜|杜拜]]度過2015年新年假期。<ref>{{cite web| last= Sarkari| first= Karishma| url= http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2895001/Not-intimate-getaway-Cody-Simpson-Gigi-Hadid-join-Selena-Gomez-beach-party-Dubai-New-Year-s-Eve-starting-2015-dip-ocean.html| title= Not such an intimate getaway! Cody Simpson and Gigi Hadid join Selena Gomez for beach party in Dubai on New Year's Eve before starting 2015 with a dip in the ocean| publisher= [[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]]| date= 2015-01-03| accessdate= 2015-03-19| archive-date= 2016-03-04| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160304114653/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2895001/Not-intimate-getaway-Cody-Simpson-Gigi-Hadid-join-Selena-Gomez-beach-party-Dubai-New-Year-s-Eve-starting-2015-dip-ocean.html| dead-url= no}}</ref>

